# Cosmon project scaffold: config and formulas are tracked; live state,
# molecule transcripts, and the registry stay local (internal working data).
.cosmon/state/
.cosmon/molecules/
.cosmon/registry.sqlite
# surfaces.toml is LOCAL-ONLY and gitignored on purpose: `cs init` auto-writes a
# live kind="github-issues" surface from the public remote (corroborated in
# runs/2026-07-22-r1prime-corroboration.md), and it must never be committed.
# scripts/guard-no-github-surface.sh fails the build if a live one appears.
# R1' verdict: maintainer deliberation 2026-07-21 — "sever the capability, don't gate the act."
.cosmon/surfaces.toml
.gitleaks.toml

# Disposable germination sandboxes and per-export artifacts.
bench/
spores/**/ro-crate-metadata.json
spores/**/states/

# Local + privately-archived; never in the public tree.
drops/
runs/

# Cosmon surface projections (derived views of internal state — local only).
STATUS.md
ISSUES.md

# Internal deliberation tooling — local only, not part of the shipped scaffold.
.cosmon/formulas/deep-think.formula.toml
